caption.text: 我愛寧靜看海。濱邊茶屋-建於新原海灘之上的橡木造茶屋，面向海邊的單邊座位，遠眺整個沙灘，感受南太平洋吹來的海風。意想不到的是，它亦為文化節表演其間的看台(舞台燈光音響都在海灘上😳. So cool ❕) 。完結一連四張淡淡然series. High contrast 也許是我一直沿用的手法，今次試下淡色一點，正好貼近最近的心情。A tea house in Southern #okinawa , built above a beach. Appreciate the beauty of the beach and feel the breeze from South Pacific. It served as a auditorium for drama performance during some festival (the stage, all lighting and audio equipment is set on a stage on the beach 😳❕) This ended my pale colour series 👉 Please look thu the grid to find my university and okinawa architecture 😊 Have a good day everyone #instagram #hkig #japan #rise #tiltshift
